title: TNF Preview, Week 9 WR/CB Matchups 2022
description:
Field Yates, Mike Clay and Daniel Dopp preview Thursday Night Football before talking the WR’s who you need to start and a running back who could be a top 10 play you need to pick up. Then, Adam Schefter joins to talk the storylines to watch in Week 9 including the impact of some key trades.
